results.name: For the n in A102783, the least k such that n divides sigma_k(n).
comment: It appears that k < n/4. Record values of k occur when n=2p, where p is a prime with primitive root 2 (A001122). In this case, k=(p-1)/2.
link: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..1000
